data.description: Wake up every morning to a peaceful lake fronting home!  This rarely available 3 bed 2 bath 2 assigned parking with separate entrance 2/1 & 0/1 gives you lots of flexibility and comfort! This home is spacious, 2 generous lanais, tastefully remodeled with lots of parking!  Owner currently rents out an additional stall that can transferred to new owners.  Conveniently located across from Schofield Barracks, shopping & more! Easy to show email & go! Hurry this won't last long! VA loan assumption rate of 2.75% is available for another VA Approved Buyer!  Motivated Seller, Make an offer!
